com.jesus_crie.modularbot_command.annotations

Annotation Type CommandInfo


  • @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface CommandInfo

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      java.lang.String[] name
      The aliases of the command.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      java.lang.String description
      A long description of the command.
      java.lang.String[] options
      The options to allow for this command.
      java.lang.String shortDescription
      A short description of the command.

    • Element Detail

      • name

        public abstract java.lang.String[] name
        The aliases of the command. The first will be the name.

      • options

        public abstract java.lang.String[] options
        The options to allow for this command. These are the names of the constants registered in Options.
        Default:
        {}

      • shortDescription

        public abstract java.lang.String shortDescription
        A short description of the command.
        Default:
        "No description."

      • description

        public abstract java.lang.String description
        A long description of the command.
        Default:
        "No description."
